$ Perl module Getopt::Long

`Getopt::Long` can be used to parse options that are passed to a perl script.

gh|PerlModules|/Getopt/Long/script.pl||

{ Default values

  gh|PerlModules|/Getopt/Long/default_value.pl||

}
{ No values

  gh|PerlModules|/Getopt/Long/no_values.pl||

}
{ Optional values

  gh|PerlModules|/Getopt/Long/optional_value.pl||

}
{ Alternative names

  gh|PerlModules|/Getopt/Long/alternative_names.pl||

}
{ Multiple values

  gh|PerlModules|/Getopt/Long/multiple_values.pl||

}
{ Hash values

  gh|PerlModules|/Getopt/Long/hash_values.pl||

}
{ Callback functions

  gh|PerlModules|/Getopt/Long/callback.pl||

}
{ Unnamed parameter

  gh|PerlModules|/Getopt/Long/unnamed_parameter.pl||

}
{ Special characters

  gh|PerlModules|/Getopt/Long/specialCharacter.pl||

}

